"msg":"張圖，send去廢老group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e92378ce4a75b8466109ee2104a5cac8448179","tid":1281224,"uid":47776,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b760ecf667a3c8a2d3c2f24465251bb12573e3a5","tid":1281224,"uid":83344,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:39:44.000Z","msg":"處理民情既方法咪係call 晒所有外圍共產團體媒體繼續污名化年青人囉<br />\n然後屈9成件事係反政府革命恫嚇中間立場既香港人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:50:53.000Z","msg":"跟手就話係顏色革命 有外國勢力支持<br />\n不容其他國家干預內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有邊次唔係咁嘅劇本<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b827f81c0f28af87629988ea602cce5708aac074","tid":1281224,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"364e047d6051a32a23e0c95c945d96eebb77205b","tid":1281224,"uid":264104,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"31c8cb9965c1ff1dd2b199e68ad4fd47e7c7953f","tid":1281224,"uid":193436,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:47:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:49:38.000Z","msg":"張圖，send去廢老group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:51:33.000Z","msg":"出左未"},{"pid":"e5c9a4c8c340b9bc6fd1c0fd092bc8dba36b057f","tid":1281224,"uid":39777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0db2a3ff8f4c904460e8c4a89ece16a8f4f436a3","tid":1281224,"uid":119478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:37:24.000Z","msg":"港人治港呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:52:51.000Z","msg":"從來都無<br />\n傀儡治港"},{"pid":"b382b77e92f7a6d36a280b5bfcd74a3db18b44c4","tid":1281224,"uid":51701,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:04:23.000Z","msg":"支那01 : 習大大係好人 薯片都係好人"},{"pid":"fde87faa